&lt;p&gt;When tuples are received, the method looks up which JCQueue to send to. It does this with the tuple destination task id. The map it looks in only has the queues by the starting task id of the executor&apos;s range, so if the destination is e.g. task 4 for an executor with assignment &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;3, 4&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;, we hit an NPE.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
